<section xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"
    xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
    <title>What is a thread</title>
    <para>
        A thread is a light-weight process with its own flow and local memory space (the thread stack) but having access
        to the application heap memory.
    </para>
